Narrator: He took a handkerchief and theatric...
en


He took a handkerchief and theatrically dabbed at his eyes.

en


"Forgive me. I was emotional for a second there."

"Good to see you too, President Smolak."

en

en


"As the Prime Minister of the Kingdom of Rizia, I hereby announce the complete annexation of the Grand Duchy of Pales, as part of the Treaty of Pales."

LineNo: 12501946,

Manus Sazon: As the Prime Minister of the Kingd...
en


"As the Prime Minister of the Kingdom of Rizia, I hereby announce the terms of the Treaty of Pales..."

en


"Finally... Duke Axel Reinhart will transfer his authority to the newly established Parliament of Pales, of which half of the representatives shall be elected by the Rizian-speaking population."

Narrator: Axel grimaced. His hair looked unwa...
en

LineNo: 12502808,

en


Axel grimaced. His hair looked unwashed and his clothes were disheveled. I wondered if he'd been rushed here straight from his cell.

en


"Well... Let's just dive into it."

LineNo: 12503290,

en


"Let's get this over with, gentlemen."

LineNo: 12503392,

Manus Sazon: The Kingdom of Rizia, as a guarant...
en


"The Kingdom of Rizia, as a guarantor of Palesian safety, will work closely with the Grand Duchy's new government to help with this transition of power."

LineNo: 12503500,

Manus Sazon: The cities of Ziqes and Arces, and...
en


"The cities of Ziqes and Arces, and the territories from the west to the new border from Navar to southern Remaz, according to the rights of the Kingdom of Rizia and the wishes of the Rizian population in these lands..."

LineNo: 12503602,

Manus Sazon: ...Will be restored back to the Ki...
en


"...Will be restored back to the Kingdom of Rizia. The border as outlined in Section B is to be recognized as the new border between Rizia and Pales and will immediately be demilitarized."

LineNo: 12503704,

Manus Sazon: Additionally, the Grand Duchy will...
en


"Additionally, the Grand Duchy will recognize the Rizian maritime borders to include the Aureus Gas Field, thereby ceding all its control and extraction rights to the Kingdom of Rizia."

LineNo: 12504084,

Beatrice Livingston (R): As the Queen of Rumburg and the ho...
en


"As the Queen of Rumburg and the host of this meeting, I would like congratulate both sides for enforcing a ceasefire. Thousands of people were expecting this for a long time."

LineNo: 12504186,

Beatrice Livingston (R): And as the mediator between Rizia...
en


"And as the mediator between Rizia and Pales, I would like to read the negotiated terms of peace as part of the Treaty of Thornborough."

LineNo: 12504288,

Beatrice Livingston (R): The Rizian and Palesian armed forc...
en


"The Rizian and Palesian armed forces will immediately withdraw from occupied territories, ensuring a return to the pre-war borders between the two countries -- to River Alca in the north."

LineNo: 12504390,

Beatrice Livingston (R): The Rizian and Palesian government...
en


"The Rizian and Palesian governments will ensure the safe return of all displaced populations as well as prisoners of war."

en


"As part of peacekeeping efforts, Rumburg will provide humanitarian aid and support both governments in their re-stabilization of the region."

en
